hopobject.body: How much notice do you have to give? buymed.info Eva Longoria's thigh-high slit wasn't the only thing that had people talking the night of the Golden Globes -- the actress also suffered an embarrassing nip-slip. While bending down to untangle her heel and Pucci gown, and clutching hairstylist Ken Paves (l.) for support, Longoria accidently flashed photographers at the InStyle and Warner Bros. Golden Globe after party at The Beverly Hilton Hotel Jan. 13, 2013.
